  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Jordan vs. Bird: One on One is a basketball video game developed by Electronic Arts as the sequel to One on One: Dr. J vs. Larry Bird from 1983. Jordan vs. Bird was initially published in 1988 for the Commodore 64 and MS-DOS, then versions were released for the Game Boy, Genesis, and Nintendo Entertainment System. The NES port was done by Rare and published by the Milton Bradley Company. There is also a handheld electronic game from Tiger Electronics.",
